reviews.text: The place is very dark, I went there on a rainy day with 3 friends.  Since it stopped raining by the time we arrived, I didn't notice that all the chairs were wet so I sat on it and my short was all wet, it's quite uncomfortable to sit there all night wearing a wet short.  The staff didn't apologise for not putting up those chairs or warn us that those are wet.  Other than that, the service was good, the server recommended an exclusive drink and shisha flavour, which was quite nice.  I enjoyed it despite the incident.
